{"code": 0, "data": [{"cid": 802552, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Alice", "pid": 166425, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "如果你一个月只花四五百 赶快去申请 如果你一个月花四五千 爬", "timestamp": 1609254346, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 802555, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Bob", "pid": 166425, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "Re Alice: 花四五千就不能申请了？", "timestamp": 1609254374, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 802560, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Carol", "pid": 166425, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "Re Bob: 本来就不能，一个月四五千算毛线个贫困啊", "timestamp": 1609254417, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 802569, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Dave", "pid": 166425, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "Re Bob: 当然…因为自己花光了钱变贫困…", "timestamp": 1609254453, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 802570, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Bob", "pid": 166425, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "Re Carol: 家庭贫困，4-5k是我自己出去赚的", "timestamp": 1609254464, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 802577, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Alice", "pid": 166425, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "Re Bob: 那您完全有能力自己赚啊，还申请个屁啊", "timestamp": 1609254513, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 802595, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Bob", "pid": 166425, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "Re Alice: 额。。希望你知道有很多拿助学金的同学是自己也有额外收入的，学校没审查这个。。", "timestamp": 1609254623, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 802629, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Carol", "pid": 166425, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "Re Bob: 严格来说不能，不过学校助学金充足我体感也不怎么存在竞争，倒也还好\n给你这样自己挣的总比给一个月家里四五千生活费的好", "timestamp": 1609254793, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 802640, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Bob", "pid": 166425, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "Re Carol: 其实审查的时候我还没有去兼职啦，这学期才开始去", "timestamp": 1609254915, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 802643, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Alice", "pid": 166425, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "Re Bob: 至少如果家庭真的贫困，一个月四五千不应该，就算你自己赚了之后存起来也行 。虽然你的钱你有支配的权利，但每个月都是四五千还是挺夸张的吧？", "timestamp": 1609254936, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 802653, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Eve", "pid": 166425, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "Re Alice: 清华助学金每年发不完，不涉及竞争指标，所以Bob的行为虽然有不妥但不恶劣。", "timestamp": 1609254996, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 802656, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Bob", "pid": 166425, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "Re Alice: 没有每个都是，也就这学期开始每个月四五千而已，挣的够补就可以安心花呀…", "timestamp": 1609255004, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 802667, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Francis", "pid": 166425, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "Re Alice: 假设一个月兼职赚1w呢hhhh", "timestamp": 1609255104, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 802679, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Bob", "pid": 166425, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "Re Francis: 差不多hhh就是搞七搞八一个月能挣个9k那种 这学期又闲", "timestamp": 1609255154, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 802724, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Alice", "pid": 166425, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "Re Bob: 其实我不是反对穷人家的孩子用钱，只是觉得至少要在自己的经济范围内花钱，如果bob挣得够多当然可以花，也和申请助学金没什么冲突，毕竟清华一年那么多钱发不掉。但是如果是花钱大手大脚妄想通过申请助学金来补贴，我觉得就很有问题了。", "timestamp": 1609255565, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 802738, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Bob", "pid": 166425, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "Re Alice: 我脱离语境回答你的，我只是想说领助学金但能赚钱的贫困同学大有人在", "timestamp": 1609255649, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 802751, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Bob", "pid": 166425, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "Re Alice: 我室友也是啊，ipad iPhone mac 全套苹果生态，人家家庭评定也是极度贫困。人家自己能搞到钱啊，家庭符合学校就会通过申请", "timestamp": 1609255708, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 802767, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Bob", "pid": 166425, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "Re Alice: 穷也是分情况的，有些贫困生是多花一分都不舍得，能存一分也要补贴家庭；但有些原生家庭都已经抛弃你了，十几年不闻不问的，有钱我给自己花给他们做甚", "timestamp": 1609255802, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 816610, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": true, "name": "洞主", "pid": 166425, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "Re Alice: 一个月一千五左右，感觉负担挺大的", "timestamp": 1609473554, "type": "text", "url": ""}], "post": {"deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "likenum": 5, "pid": 166425, "reply": 19, "tag": null, "text": "感觉生活费要爆表了，像申请贫困助学金", "timestamp": 1609254215, "type": "text", "updated_at": 1609473553, "url": "", "vote": {}}}